title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 5000
description:
5000 and getting near the last of the letter B.   250 more CDG+MP3 Karaoke songs from the Rigmar Radio working commercial Karaoke collection which has been purchased over many, many years with some hard to get tracks obtained from sites like this.

The collection has been re named and the MP3 files tagged for correct search results when playing back on a PC or Mac which alone makes it stand out from all the other Karaoke uploads you see posted on bit torrent sites.

No backwards file names,  No Karaoke label index numbers which of course import in the Artist field on a PC or Mac.

Industry convention for the naming of Music files are quite clear on this fact:

Any music file should take the format of Artist - Song Title [Any other info]

NOT SC105883_Jones,_Tom_._Green_Green_Grass_Of_Home
 OR SF1085348 - Hello - Adele

and all the other nonsense you see posted all the time.  Enjoy:

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
